{"id":860085303,"question_id":3,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 6 months","timestamp":1671092739,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"7 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/860085303/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"42.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        HashSet<Character> set = new HashSet<>();\n        int max = 0;\n        int st =0;\n        for(int ed=0; ed<s.length(); ed++){\n            \n            char ch = s.charAt(ed);\n            while(set.contains(ch)){\n                set.remove(s.charAt(st));\n                st++;\n            }\n            \n            set.add(ch);\n            \n            max = Math.max(max, ed-st+1);\n        }\n        \n        return max;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
